OL,3,CSeven men arrested after 'violent
OL,4,Cdisorder' on street
OL,6,FSeven men have been arrested after
OL,7,Ffighting broke out on a city centre
OL,8,Fstreet, Gwent Police said.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to Commercial
OL,11,FRoad, Newport, after a group of men
OL,12,Fwere seen fighting in the street at
OL,13,Faround 3.20pm on Friday 1 August.
OL,15,FSix men, aged 25, 28, 33, 40, 42 and
OL,16,F52, and one 17-year-old boy, who are
OL,17,Fall from Newport, were arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of violent disorder. They
OL,19,Fremain in custody.
