OL,6,FFour of the men attended hospital, two
OL,7,Fwere later discharged while two others
OL,8,Fremain in hospital receiving treatment.
OL,10,FChief Superintendent John Davies said:
OL,11,F"We will not tolerate anyone who acts
OL,12,Fin such a violent way on our streets,
OL,13,For exposes members of our communities
OL,14,Fto such a horrific level of aggression
OL,15,Fwhen they go about their daily
OL,16,Fbusiness.
