OL,6,F"Violence in any form is completely
OL,7,Funacceptable, and we have acted
OL,8,Fdecisively in making these arrests.
OL,9,FAnyone else who is found to be
OL,10,Finvolved in this violent disorder will
OL,11,Falso be dealt with.
OL,13,F"This is now a live investigation and
OL,14,Fspeculation, especially online and
OL,15,Fsocial media commentary, about the
OL,16,Fidentities of those involved will not
OL,17,Fhelp us secure justice against those
OL,18,Ffound to be responsible."
